，專家仍嘗試填補佩特拉空白的歷史、揭示箇中奧秘。利用最現代化的技術，專家會剖析這件古建築家的作品。盡以不同程度，不同角度，從遠到近審視佩特拉，找出肉眼看不到的證據。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/ancientsuperstructures/originals/mfile_8918_682599_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fancientsuperstructures%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8918_682599_1_l.jpg&h=9fd58a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/ancientsuperstructures/originals/mfile_8918_682599_4_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fancientsuperstructures%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8918_682599_4_l.jpg&h=79fc410f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙語廣播：粵語/英語 (電視版)<br />\n播放頻道：港台電視 31、31A<br />\n播出時間：(首播)<br />\n(重溫)<br />\n<br />\n2020年6月23日 星期二 晚上9時30分<br />\n2020年6月24日 星期三 凌晨12時      <br />\n2020年6月24日 星期三 中午12時"},{"pid":"375d4645e013e93d66cc062b26bb5f977f46b95f","tid":2054821,"uid":30,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d82f91596ffa8f6ebf4a6334f809c2c31e14a88","tid":2054821,"uid":30,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55b85b65106b1f599b23b284abcfd06660a152f","tid":2054821,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab2e28d0b001ee07becfc5ef76a6626c75ed51f","tid":2054821,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0