g/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fancientsuperstructures%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8918_683633_1_l.jpg&h=8a27fa3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/ancientsuperstructures/originals/mfile_8918_683633_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fancientsuperstructures%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8918_683633_3_l.jpg&h=8ed22a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/ancientsuperstructures/originals/mfile_8918_683633_9_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fancientsuperstructures%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8918_683633_9_l.jpg&h=99f0bacb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7Pv1930By0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm7Pv1930By0&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=37e58cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7Pv1930By0</a><br />\n<br />\n地球最大洲之上，萬里長城橫跨中國東、西部。有世界第七大奇蹟之稱的長城，二千年來由世世代代的中國建築家參與興建，這座偉大建築的神秘面紗卻依舊未揭開。<br />\n<br />\n引用今天最先進的科技，專家能夠仔細端詳這座聯合國教科文組織古蹟，剖析古建築家的建築技藝，揭示數千年來箇中秘密。萬里長城長又長，長城到底有多長？它千年來屹立不倒的秘密又是甚麼？多角度細看長城，見微知著，專家找出肉眼不見的細節。歷史、科學、建築&hellip;將中國萬里長城的古老奧秘一一解構。<br />\n<br />\n 雙語廣播：粵語/英語 (電視版)<br />\n播放頻道：港台電視 31、31A<br />\n播出時間：(首播)(重溫)2020年7月7日 星期二 晚上9時30分<br />\n2020年7月8日 星期三 凌晨12時      <br />\n2020年7月8日 星期三 中午12時"},{"pid":"8b0e705c1f0e4749250b0c3eaf87ac4a2b21309e","tid":2054821,"uid":74783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bee5519cd3bcce9a154946dfe6f61885badb4c4","tid":2054821,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"支那"},{"pid":"bf4dc517ce631a714f65e2e02210fdb5b8628535","ti